    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking and driving just like it did when it first left the lot. It\u2019s been kept spotless and babied every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this beauty to go to a great new home! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
