    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in flawless shape without a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will love it as much as I have, so I\u2019ve priced it to move fast. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
